<p>So I am trying to pass the cookies after I have authenticated a user. Here is my code to try to add the cookie to the request:</p>  <pre><code>func makeHTTPGetRequest(path: String, onCompletion: ServiceResponse) {     let request = NSMutableURLRequest(URL: NSURL(string: path)!)     let session = NSURLSession.sharedSession()      request.addValue("\"cookie\"", forHTTPHeaderField: "\"Set-Cookie\"")      println(request.allHTTPHeaderFields)     let task = session.dataTaskWithRequest(request, completionHandler: {data, response, error -&gt; Void in         println(response)          let json:JSON = JSON(data: data)         onCompletion(json, error)     })     task.resume() } </code></pre>  <p>I use request.addValue to add the cookie to the header, but this does not seem to go through after the request is made.</p>